snippet.title: Colin McRae Rally 3 - Game Trailer (2002)
snippet.description:
Colin McRae Rally 3 -  official trailer video
Developped by Codemasters
Published by  Codemasters  in 2002 for Playstation 2 and Xbox, then in 2003 for PC (Windows)
PC version ported by  Six by Nine Ltd
System : PS2/Xbox/PC
Year : 2002 (PS2/Xbox), 2003 (PC)
Trailer found on the 'I.G.I 2 Covert Strike'  game disc
